snippet.title: Longplay of Barbie: Magic Genie Adventure
snippet.description:
Longplay of Barbie: Magic Genie Adventure, played as the NTSC version on the Game Boy Color. This game's version was released on Nov. 11th, 2000. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

00:00​ - Start
01:12 - Crystal City
08:07 - Magical Forest
12:56 - City Of Clouds
16:50 - Dragon Playground
23:51 - Hidden Atlantis
30:44 - Kardal's Palace
39:43 - End

By: Terua
